ns, Cat ... v ..\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f51/1/16/2714.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" />  Supply of synchronous cabinets (SYS) and ATS cabinets.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f51/1/16/2714.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" />  Provide soundproof enclosures and sound insulation for generators.\r\n\r\nCompany We have provided many soundproofing system for typical generator such as Gem Center (No.8 Nguyen Binh Khiem, Da Kao Ward, District 1, Vietinbank tower (93-95 Ham Nghi, Ward Nguyen Thai Binh, District 1), VBB tower (vietcombank tower) (No 2, Me Linh Square, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City), Vung Tau International Convention Center 2300 Kva (Himoinsa) backup station at Hiep Phuoc and Cai Mep Ports, AIS (American International School), Nha Be District, AIS (American International School), Nguyen Van Cu, District 1 ... and many others.\r\n\r\n<strong>STC VIETNAM ENGINEERING TECHNOLOGY CO.,LTD</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Add : F 1 -  Packsimex tower - 52 Dong Du - Bennghe .W, 1 Dis, Hochiminh City</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Code Tax : 0 3 1 3 2 5 6 5 7 8</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Email : stcvietnam@247dichvu.com, sales.247dichvu@gmail.com</strong>[:]', 'Giới thiệu', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '68-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-14 14:25:59', '2018-05-14 07:25:59', '', 68, 'http://myhome.local/68-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
